      .page
        .section#grid
          .row-fluid
            .span10
              .widget
                .widget-header
                  i.icon-th
                  h3 Layout Grid

                .widget-content
                  :markdown
                    While your still open to use the 5px grid defined in the __WIMP Guidelines__ , we 
                    recommend giving up a strict 5px pixel finegrained grid.

                    Instead we recommend using the grid system defined in twitter bootstrap:

                    - [940px base - 12 columns](#{path}bootstrap/scaffolding.html#gridSystem)
                    - [responsive - 12 columns](#{path}bootstrap/scaffolding.html#fluidGridSystem)
                  
        .section#logo
          .row-fluid
            .span10
              .widget
                .widget-header
                  h3 Usage of the kaba logo

                .widget-content
                  :markdown
                    Take into account that for the logo usage the same rules must be applied as in the 
                    print guidelines (color usage, proportions and raster usage).

                    The logos for using in the software come in 3 different sizes:

                  .row-fluid
                    .span4
                      h6 40px height:
                      img.img-border(src="#{path}public/img/kaba_xs.gif")
                    .span4
                      h6 60px height:
                      img.img-border(src="#{path}public/img/kaba_s.gif")
                    .span4
                      h6 80px height:
                      img.img-border(src="#{path}public/img/kaba.gif")



